Title: Miles 10 Titanfall 2 Replay Demo
Description:
This is a short video demonstrating the replay functionality of Miles 10!

During the game, a file is saved to disc, capturing all input from the game to the Miles runtime. Miles Studio lets you replay these files, which is great for bug reproducing and iteration! The game itself is not loaded - only the Miles Studio project.

Special thanks to Respawn for allowing us to release this video.

Note that this is not retail content, and so audio will not match what you would hear in the released game.

Title: A Cancel Culture Glossary
Description: Every day, I check my twitter feed, and sure enough, every day, it greets me with another Cancelling. A Cancelling is, generally speaking, any time people on the internet join together to express negative emotions and opinions about someone or something. Many people believe that the purpose of a Cancelling is to Ruin A Life. It might be over an offensive tweet. A movie with a problematic premise. A racist caught on tape. Or in some cases, an actual criminal being exposed for his or her illegal actions. The frequency of these Cancellings have also given rise to the term “Cancel Culture.”
